data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. -SELLER MOTIVATED - Nestled in Deltona, Florida known for its natural beauty due to its proximity to numerous lakes, parks, and natural areas making it great for recreational outdoor activities such as boating, fishing, hiking, and biking. This charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home exudes coziness and modern style. With a vinyl fenced backyard that looks over the pond behind the home. The home offers an the interior of fresh and contemporary. The kitchen offers an open floorplan with eat in space which opens up to the Dining Room. Outside, a tranquil backyard awaits complete with majestic trees and a screened-in lanai. Conveniently located, this home is a perfect blend of comfort and practicality in a desirable area within reasonable driving distance of Orlando's attractions, including theme parks like Walt Disney World and Universal Studios. This home is also close to beaches such as New Smyrna and major highways like Interstate 4 for easy commuting. Schedule your showing today!
